data.description: Cute and charming describe this nicely maintained Duplex in Irvington. Some updates but mostly original. Spacious kitchen with eating area. Heat for house is a gas stove as well as wall heaters. Attached studio at back of house with separate entrance is currently occupied and rented. Main home was owner occupied so no rent to show.  Pictures are of main house only. Main house address is 2144. Studio is 2148.
